data.description: Nestled in the Astoria Trails South gated community, this exceptional split-level residence awaits your discovery. As you step inside, your attention is immediately drawn to the exquisite rich wood flooring. Descending a few steps, you'll find the downstairs area with three bedrooms and a den/office space. Ascending, you'll encounter the inviting family room, well-appointed kitchen, and the primary bedroom. The generously proportioned family room seamlessly connects to a thoughtfully designed kitchen featuring granite countertops, upgraded cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Outside, the rear of the property boasts a covered patio, pergola and an above-ground pool creating an ideal space for outdoor relaxation and entertainment. Opportunities like this should not be missed! This fantastic home offers convenient access to nearby schools, shopping centers, freeways, and​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ parks.
